<div class="min-h-screen">
  <!-- Header -->
  <div class="bg-gray-900 border-b border-gray-800">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-3">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
        <h1 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white">About Project</h1>
        
        <!-- Navigation Links -->
        <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
          <%= link_to root_path, class: "text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors" do %>
            Tasks
          <% end %>
          <%= link_to contacts_path, class: "text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-white transition-colors" do %>
            Contacts
          <% end %>
        </div>
        
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <%= button_to "Exit", session_path, method: :delete,
            class: "px-3 py-1.5 text-xs text-gray-400 hover:text-red-400 transition-colors" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl py-8 px-4">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-blue-600 rounded-full mb-4">
        <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Time Tracker</h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        A simple and efficient task management application with real-time tracking capabilities. Create tasks, track time, and organize your work with intuitive filtering and pagination.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Features Grid -->
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
      <div class="glass-card p-6 hover-lift">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Task Management</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-400">Create up to 20 tasks with titles and descriptions. Mark tasks as finished when completed.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-card p-6 hover-lift">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-blue-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Real-time Timers</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-400">Start/stop timers for each task with up to 3 concurrent active timers. Automatic time calculation and display.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-card p-6 hover-lift">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-purple-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 4a1 1 0 011-1h16a1 1 0 011 1v2.586a1 1 0 01-.293.707l-6.414 6.414a1 1 0 00-.293.707V17l-4 4v-6.586a1 1 0 00-.293-.707L3.293 7.293A1 1 0 013 6.586V4z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Smart Filtering</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-400">Filter tasks by status: New (never started), Active (currently running), Done (completed), or view All tasks.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-card p-6 hover-lift">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-orange-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Time Logging</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-400">Automatic daily log creation with start/end times. Track total time spent on each task and daily progress.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-card p-6 hover-lift">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-indigo-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 21h10a2 2 0 002-2V9.414a1 1 0 00-.293-.707l-5.414-5.414A1 1 0 0012.586 3H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Pagination</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-400">Clean interface with 4 tasks per page using Pagy gem for efficient browsing of your task list.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="glass-card p-6 hover-lift">
        <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-green-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mr-3">
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">User Authentication</h3>
        </div>
        <p class="text-gray-400">Secure user registration and login system with bcrypt password hashing and session management.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Tech Stack -->
    <div class="glass-card p-8 mb-12">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-6 text-center">Built With</h3>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto mb-3 bg-red-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">RB</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-white font-medium">Ruby on Rails 8</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">MVC Framework</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto mb-3 bg-blue-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">TW</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-white font-medium">Tailwind CSS</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Utility-First CSS</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto mb-3 bg-purple-500 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">ST</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-white font-medium">Stimulus + Turbo</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Hotwire Stack</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 mx-auto mb-3 bg-gray-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-white font-bold text-sm">DB</span>
          </div>
          <h4 class="text-white font-medium">SQLite</h4>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Database</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Additional gems -->
      <div class="mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-gray-700">
        <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-4 text-center">Key Dependencies</h4>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-3">
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-800 text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full">BCrypt (Authentication)</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-800 text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full">Pagy (Pagination)</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-800 text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full">Solid Cache/Queue</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-800 text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full">Kamal (Deployment)</span>
          <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-800 text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-full">RSpec (Testing)</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Project Info -->
    <div class="glass-card p-8 text-center">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">How It Works</h3>
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <p class="text-gray-300 mb-4">
          This Time Tracker is a focused productivity tool built with Ruby on Rails 8. It allows you to create tasks (called "deeds"), 
          track time spent on each task using start/stop timers, and organize your work efficiently.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-4">
          Key features include: task creation with titles and descriptions, real-time timer functionality with up to 3 concurrent active timers, 
          automatic time calculation and logging, smart filtering (New/Active/Done/All), and paginated task display for better organization.
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-6">
          The application includes user authentication, limits of 20 tasks per user for focused productivity, and a clean, responsive dark interface 
          built with Tailwind CSS. All timer data is automatically saved with precise start/end timestamps.
        </p>
        <div class="flex justify-center items-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-400">
          <span>Rails 8.0.1</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>Ruby 3.3+</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>SQLite Database</span>
          <span>•</span>
          <span>Docker Ready</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
